Bulletins.BulletinTitle: Sea/BI - Wenatchee to replace Walla Walla on Friday, November 7
Bulletins.BulletinText: After successful repairs, the Wenatchee will return to the Seattle/Bainbridge route on Friday, Nov. 7, replacing the Walla Walla as the #1 vessel. We do not expect service impacts during this vessel swap. Thank you for your patience as we repair our vessels.

Bulletins.BulletinTitle: Regular Schedule on Veterans Day, Tuesday, Nov 11
Bulletins.BulletinText: We are running a regular Tuesday schedule on Veterans Day, Tuesday, Nov. 11. Visit our schedules webpage to view your route schedule and learn more about our holiday schedules.
